description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Yonaguni horse on Yonaguni Island, Japan
-Kiso horse in front of Mt.Ontake, Japan
-A horse in a field of azaleas
-Satsuma Fuji and a herd of horses
-Wild horses in Cape Toimisaki, Japan
-A horse in the Balskhorn Valley, Kyrgyzstan
-Kiso horse in Kaida Kogen, Japan
-A winter horse in Hokkaido, Japan
-Horses in Aso, Japan
-Grazing Landscape in South Gobi, Mongolia
name: Scenes with Horses
